item.title: CVE-2020-5544|2024-08-04T08:30:24.508Z -- mitsubishi%20electric%20corporation -- mitsubishi%20electric%20melqic%20iu1%20series
item.description: Null Pointer Dereference vulnerability in TCP function included in the firmware of Mitsubishi Electric MELQIC IU1 series IU1-1M20-D firmware version 1.0.7 and earlier allows remote attackers to stop the network functions or execute malware via a specially crafted packet.

item.description: TCP function included in the firmware of Mitsubishi Electric MELQIC IU1 series IU1-1M20-D firmware version 1.0.7 and earlier allows remote attackers to bypass access restriction and to stop the network functions or execute malware via a specially crafted packet.
